graphics-nacl
=============
INSTALL 
1.1 Install NaCl SDK (https://developer.chrome.com/native-client/sdk/download)
export NACL_SDK_ROOT=<nacl_sdk_dir/pepper_ver>
1.2 Install naclports 
Download depot_tools
git clone https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/tools/depot_tools.git
export PATH=<depot_tools_dir>:"$PATH"
mkdir naclports
cd naclports
gclient config --name=src  https://chromium.googlesource.com/external/naclports.git@pepper_<pepper_ver>
gclient sync
1.2.1 Install libpng
./src/bin/naclports install libpng --toolchain=pnacl --arch=pnacl
1.3 Download ddjvu (https://github.com/ipotuzhnov/ddjvu.git)
export DDJVU_ROOT=<ddjvu_dir>
1.4 Install nacl-djvulibre (https://github.com/ipotuzhnov/nacl-djvulibre-3.5.35.git) follow README_NaCl instructions.
export DJVULIBRE_ROOT=<nacl_djvulibre_dir>
2. Run nacl-env nacl-make

DEBUGGING
1. Useful links
Debugging via Eclipse 
1.1 http://digilancer.com/?p=34
1.2 http://www.chromium.org/nativeclient/how-tos/debugging-documentation/debugging-with-debug-stub-recommended/debugging-nacl-apps-in-eclipse-cdt
